# Primer Server 2
## Install

	pip3 install primerserver2
	
Design genome-wide specific PCR primers.

## Input

	- Candidate Primers by Primer3
	- BLAST
	- Nucleotide Thermodynamics
	
## Output

	- Possible amplicons and primers for each site
	
## Dependencies

Python 3.8, [git clone https://github.com/samtools/samtools](Samtools) to convert fastq 2 BAM/CRAM, WDS/WES 2 VCF and manipulation of these formats. [git clone https://github.com/samtools/htslib](Here) and bcftools are needed too. 

[sudo apt install ncbi-blast+](Blast) is easily accesed from NCBI's web page and from terminal. 